data.description:
This recently remodeled home in West Mifflin is fully move in ready & features a MUST SEE backyard! Situated on a double lot, this home has two (possibly 4 if need be) concrete off street parking spaces & a huge fully fenced in backyard, ready to contain the pups. Upon entering, you'll be at ease knowing the entire home was renovated just a few years ago. The layout provides flexibility for how you utilize the space; the front room can be an office, play room, living area or dedicated dining room. The kitchen features timeless white shaker cabinets, stainless appliance & an island that provides an open concept design. The main floor is completed with a convenient full bath. The second level has a spacious primary bedroom & second bedroom, as well as another full bath. The third floor bedroom would make an awesome teenage bedroom or second living space. The full basement is clean & dry. Close to public transportation, shopping & dining at the waterfront & Century 3. Easy drive to downtown & 376. Dogs and cats are welcome upon approval. To be considered as a tenant please send an application.

Unfurnished, Renter's/ tenant's are responsible for all utilities and lawn-care/ snow removal.
